### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### ============================================
### PACIENTES
### ============================================

### Crear Paciente
POST {{baseUrl}}/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Diego López",
  "email": "diego@example.com",
  "phone": "5551234567",
  "age": 30,
  "medicalHistory": "Ninguno"
}

### Obtener todos los pacientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients

### Obtener paciente por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients/PATIENT_ID_HERE

### Actualizar paciente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/patients/PATIENT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "medicalHistory": "Hipertensión"
}

### Eliminar paciente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/patients/PATIENT_ID_HERE

### ============================================
### DOCTORES
### ============================================

### Crear Doctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Juan Martínez",
  "specialty": "Cardiología",
  "email": "juan.martinez@hospital.com",
  "phone": "5559876543",
  "scheduleStart": "08:00",
  "scheduleEnd": "17:00",
  "daysAvailable": [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]
}

### Obtener todos los doctores
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors

### Obtener doctores por especialidad
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors?specialty=Cardiología

### Obtener doctor por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors/DOCTOR_ID_HERE

### Actualizar doctor
PUT {{baseUrl}}/doctors/DOCTOR_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "5551234567"
}

### Eliminar doctor
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/doctors/DOCTOR_ID_HERE

### ============================================
### CITAS MÉDICAS
### ============================================

### Crear Cita
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "PATIENT_ID_HERE",
  "doctorId": "DOCTOR_ID_HERE",
  "dateTime": "2024-01-20T10:30:00Z",
  "reason": "Chequeo general"
}

### Obtener todas las citas
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments

### Obtener citas por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments?status=scheduled

### Obtener citas por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31

### Obtener citas de un paciente
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/patient/PATIENT_ID_HERE

### Obtener citas de un doctor
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/doctor/DOCTOR_ID_HERE

### Verificar disponibilidad del doctor
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/availability?doctorId=DOCTOR_ID_HERE&date=2024-01-20

### Actualizar cita
PUT {{baseUrl}}/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dateTime": "2024-01-21T14:00:00Z",
  "reason": "Chequeo completo",
  "notes": "Llevar análisis previos"
}

### Cancelar cita (DELETE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID_HERE

### ============================================
### INFORMACIÓN
### ============================================

### API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}
